<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Devout" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Devout,</orth> pious, religious: <bibl n="shak. tn 3.4.424" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 4, 424</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 5.4.48" default="NO" valid="yes">John V, 4, 48</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 1.1.9" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 I, 1, 9</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.7.92" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 7, 92</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 2.3.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 3, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.2.93" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 2, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.4.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 4, 41</bibl>. <cit><quote>but more d. than this in our respects have we not been,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.792" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 792</bibl></cit> (i. e. we have not treated the business as a matter of holy importance).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>